    52("<div style='font-weight: bold'>Transparency log (Rekor)</div><div style='font-size: 70%; margin-top: 0px'>[Software System]</div><div style='font-size: 80%; margin-top:10px'>Optional append-only<br />signature log; blank in<br />air-gapped orgs. houba can<br />point at one but never<br />deploys it.</div>")
    style 52 fill:#0f766e,stroke:#0a524d,color:#ffffff
    53("<div style='font-weight: bold'>Upstream Scanner</div><div style='font-size: 70%; margin-top: 0px'>[Software System]</div><div style='font-size: 80%; margin-top:10px'>Produces vulnerability / EOL<br />scan reports (CI pipeline,<br />registry-native scanner, or<br />scan service). houba ingests<br />the report; it never calls<br />the scanner.</div>")
